casebody.data:
Thomas J. PRESLEY, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Missouri, Respondent. WD 81568 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. Order filed: July 30, 2019 Gregory L. Barnes, Jefferson City, for Respondent. Christian Lehmberg, for Appellant. Before Division Three: Gary D. Witt, Presiding Judge, Edward R. Ardini, Jr., Judge and Thomas N. Chapman, Judge

ORDER

PER CURIAM:

Thomas Presley appeals the judgment of the Circuit Court of Cass County denying his Rule 29.15 motion for post-conviction relief. Finding no error, we affirm. Because a published opinion would have no precedential value, we have instead provided a memorandum of law to the parties. Rule 84.16(b).
